<h1>Design Process 🚀</h1>
<h2>Here you'll find my workflow when working on a website project, from the first meeting to the actual delivery. This is the way I work with my clients.</h2>

<h3 class="title">1 First meeting 🤝</h3>
<p>Let's talk to see if we're a good fit. In person or video call.</p>
<p>We'll go from sharyour basic need to an in-depth questionnaire about your business, your goals, and any particular feature you may require for your website.</p>

<h3 class="title">2 Proposal ✍️</h3>
<p>I'll send you a proposal that includes everything we have talked about.</p>

<h3 class="title">3 Brand Understanding 🧠</h3>
<p>Exceptional websites start by understanding your requirements. I’ll ask you questions to understand your image, goals, target markets, content requirements, reference sites, materials and desired outcomes. Basically, we’ll cover everything you
  know and want at this point.</p>
<p>Once I’ve learned what you need, it’s time to start planning how I'm going to make it happen. I’ll map out your sites architecture, defining sections and pages including their flow and relationship to each other. I’ll create a functional
  specifications that sets out in detail the things your website must do, and how it will do them.</p>
